					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Confrontation between the Castilian and Aragonese crowns</div>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Not to be confused with <a href="/wiki/War_of_the_Peters" title="War of the Peters">War of the Peters</a>.</div>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r963460841">@media all and (min-width:720px){.mw-parser-output .desktop-float-right{box-sizing:border-box;float:right;clear:right}}.mw-parser-output .infobox.vevent .status>p:first-child{margin:0}</style><table class="infobox vevent" style="width:25.5em;border-spacing:2px;"><tbody><tr><th class="summary" colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">War of the Two Peters</th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="background-color:#DCDCDC;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;">Part of the <a href="/wiki/Hundred_Years%27_War" title="Hundred Years&#39; War">Hundred Years' War</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2"><table style="width:100%;margin:0;padding:0;border:0;display:inline-table"><tbody><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Date</th><td>1356–1375</td></tr><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Location</th><td><div class="location">Mostly towns in the <a href="/wiki/Kingdom_of_Aragon" title="Kingdom of Aragon">Kingdom of Aragon</a> and the <a href="/wiki/Kingdom_of_Valencia" title="Kingdom of Valencia">Kingdom of Valencia</a>, coast of the <a href="/wiki/Principality_of_Catalonia" title="Principality of Catalonia">Principality of Catalonia</a></div></td></tr><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Result</th><td class="status">
<p>Trastámarian victory
</p>
<ul><li>Overthrow of <a href="/wiki/Peter_of_Castile" title="Peter of Castile">Peter of Castile</a></li>
<li>Accession of <a href="/wiki/Henry_II_of_Castile" title="Henry II of Castile">Henry II of Castile</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Belligerents</th></tr><tr><td style="width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">
<p><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Crown_of_Castile_(1284-1390).svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/15/Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Crown_of_Castile_%281284-1390%29.svg/20px-Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Crown_of_Castile_%281284-1390%29.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="24" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/15/Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Crown_of_Castile_%281284-1390%29.svg/30px-Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Crown_of_Castile_%281284-1390%29.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/15/Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Crown_of_Castile_%281284-1390%29.svg/40px-Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Crown_of_Castile_%281284-1390%29.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="772" data-file-height="924" /></a></span> <b><a href="/wiki/Crown_of_Castile" title="Crown of Castile">Crown of Castile</a></b><br />
</p>
<i>With the support of:</i><br /><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Royal_Arms_of_England_(1340-1367).svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/Royal_Arms_of_England_%281340-1367%29.svg/15px-Royal_Arms_of_England_%281340-1367%29.svg.png" decoding="async" width="15" height="17" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/Royal_Arms_of_England_%281340-1367%29.svg/23px-Royal_Arms_of_England_%281340-1367%29.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/Royal_Arms_of_England_%281340-1367%29.svg/30px-Royal_Arms_of_England_%281340-1367%29.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="410" data-file-height="478" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Kingdom_of_England" title="Kingdom of England">Kingdom of England</a><br /><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:CoA_civ_ITA_milano.png" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/CoA_civ_ITA_milano.png/15px-CoA_civ_ITA_milano.png" decoding="async" width="15" height="19" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/CoA_civ_ITA_milano.png/23px-CoA_civ_ITA_milano.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/CoA_civ_ITA_milano.png/30px-CoA_civ_ITA_milano.png 2x" data-file-width="400" data-file-height="514" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Republic_of_Genoa" title="Republic of Genoa">Republic of Genoa</a><br /><span class="mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:PortugueseFlag1248.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/PortugueseFlag1248.svg/15px-PortugueseFlag1248.svg.png" decoding="async" width="15" height="15" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/PortugueseFlag1248.svg/23px-PortugueseFlag1248.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/PortugueseFlag1248.svg/30px-PortugueseFlag1248.svg.png 2x" data